---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="border-t border-white/10 py-10">
	<div class="grid-shell">
		<div class="panel flex flex-col gap-8 px-6 py-8 sm:px-8 lg:flex-row lg:items-center lg:justify-between">
			<div class="max-w-2xl">
				<p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-cyan-300">
					Portfolio + Blog + Writeups
				</p>
				<h2 class="mt-3 text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-50">
					Building secure systems and documenting the lessons worth keeping.
				</h2>
				<p class="mt-3 max-w-xl text-sm leading-7 text-slate-400">
					A static Astro site for projects, technical notes, and CTF-style writeups that stay easy
					to maintain and fast to deploy.
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="flex flex-col gap-3 text-sm text-slate-400">
				<a
					href="https://github.com/ashuraweismann"
					target="_blank"
					rel="noreferrer"
					class="transition hover:text-cyan-200"
				>
					GitHub
				</a>
				<a
					href="https://www.linkedin.com"
					target="_blank"
					rel="noreferrer"
					class="transition hover:text-cyan-200"
				>
					LinkedIn
				</a>
				<a href="/rss.xml" class="transition hover:text-cyan-200">RSS Feed</a>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="mt-4 flex flex-col gap-2 text-xs text-slate-500 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between">
			<p>&copy; {year} Ashura Weismann. All rights reserved.</p>
			<p>Designed with Astro, Tailwind CSS, and a bias toward clean engineering notes.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</footer>
